Packages 
Package Description
org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis
This is the top-level package for the AGCL plug-in.
org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.actions
This package provides actions that are executed when the user clicks on one of the plug-in buttons or menu options.
org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.actions.concrete  
org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.algorithms
This package contains the actual analysis algorithms executed by the AGCL analysis plug-in.
org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.algorithms.concrete  
org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.config
This package contains definitions to manage the plugin's preferences.
org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.misc
This package contains only drafts of code or deprecated code.
org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.results
This package contains classes to manage analysis results.
org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.util
This package contains utility classes and functions.
org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.verifiers
This package contains the main verification framework that links the algorithms from the org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.algorithms package to an external (PSL) verifier.
org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.verifiers.impl  
org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.verifiers.util  
org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.visitors
This package contains visitors (Ecore switches) for processing the AADL models and the AGCL clauses.
org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.visitors.concrete
